Welcome home to this beautifully updated split level in North Ridgeville ! Upon entry, you'll notice the newer vinyl flooring (2019) in the living room and leading to the kitchen. These spaces have been reconfigured to create an open floorplan. The entire kitchen has been remodeled (2019) and has plenty of cabinet and counter space and barstool seating. The lower level has newer tile flooring (2019) and a half bathroom. Upstairs is a remodeled full bathroom and three generous sized bedrooms, with recent vinyl flooring (2022) installed. The detached two-car garage has a workshop area and plenty of storage space. This move-in ready home is located on the northeast side of North Ridgeville, close to the amenities and highway access of neighboring communities.<br>
<br>
No pets, no smoking, no section 8. Lease is for one year. Tenants pay utilities and keep up the yard.
